<h3>Flooring:</h3>
<p>When deciding on what type of flooring works best for you, you should take a few things into consideration.</p>
<ul>
    <li>Will you need as much head room as possible?</li>
    <li>Are you going to need something that is extra durable?</li>
    <li>Are you going to spend time in climates with lots of moisture?</li>
</ul>


